headline: UBS Maintains “Neutral” on Conagra (CAG), Lowers Price Target to $20
summary: Conagra Brands, Inc. (NYSE:CAG) is one of the best alternative meat stocks to invest in according to analysts. On July 11, UBS maintained a “Neutral” rating on Conagra’s stock and lowered the price target on the shares to $20 from $21. Analyst Bryan Adams stated that his decision takes into account the company’s “less-than-stellar performance […]
